HEADWORD: Marmolite
<hw>Mar"mo*lite</hw> <pr>(m⟦aum⟧r"m⟦osl⟧*l⟦imac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Gr. <grk>maramai`rein</grk> to sparkle + <ets>-lite</ets>.]</ety>
